<p>Reports missing <code>exec</code> in the shell form of ENTRYPOINT command.</p>
<p>
  To ensure that <code>docker stop</code> will signal any long running ENTRYPOINT executable correctly,
  it needs to be started with <code>exec</code>.
</p>
<p>
  See <a href="https://docs.docker.com/reference/dockerfile/#shell-form-entrypoint-example">Dockerfile reference</a> for more information.
</p>
